MINIMUM VIABLE PRODUCT
_	Owner should be able to...
	x FACILITY
		x create / edit
		x add rooms or make them inactive
		_ unassociate themselves from a facility
	_ STAFF
		_ add users with staff/admin roles
		x	assign users to facilities
		_ archive users & disable priveleges
		_ promote / demote users (except other Execs)
		_	remove users from facilities (except other Execs, or only Facility creator can do this?)
=======================================================
_	Owner / Admin should be able to...
	_ PAYMENTS
		x	see total payments upcoming
		x	see total payments past due
		_	mark a payment as deposited
		_	have payment reminders sent to resident POAs/Reps on a monthly basis?
		_	have payment confirmations sent to resident POAs/Reps on a monthly basis?
	x	INVOICES
		x Edit invoices w/ notes - single line item
		x	Create new invoice
		x	Delete invoice

_	Admin / Owner / Staff should be able to
	x	see all maintenance requests ordered by facility
	x	see only their respective facility maintenance issues
	x	mark maintenance request as Low / High priority, or Emergency
		_	w/ a text notification to the maintenance person
	x	mark maintenance request as completed

